5,"The Space segment absorbed $3,004M of Starship R&D in FY2025 against $4,086M of segment revenue. If that Starship R&D were treated as an unallocated corporate expense instead of segment expense, what would Space Segment Adjusted EBITDA be? What does this indicate about segment-level profitability presentation?",quantitative,Segment economics and operating performance,,Accounting and transaction advisory,Cost-allocation judgment affecting segment profitability presentation.
6,"The AI segment generated $3,201M of FY2025 revenue. Identify which AI sub-components are disclosed with revenue granularity and which are not. What does the level of disclosure permit and not permit an analyst to conclude about Grok monetization?",disclosure,KPI quality and monetization,,Venture and growth investing,Monetization disclosure granularity for Grok.
7,"As of March 31, 2026, SpaceX disclosed approximately 9,600 broadband satellites supporting 10.3M Starlink subscribers and approximately 650 V1 Mobile satellites supporting 7.4M monthly unique satellite-to-mobile devices. Calculate the users-per-satellite ratio for each network and explain the utilization implications.",quantitative,KPI quality and monetization,,Public-market investing,Operating-KPI construction (utilization ratio).
