16,"The preliminary filing omits IPO price range and final share count. Which of the following can be determined from the filing as filed and which require amendment disclosure: (i) post-IPO fully diluted share count, (ii) Class A versus Class B economic ownership, and (iii) Musk's post-IPO voting control?",disclosure,Valuation and underwriting analysis,Governance and control structures,Securities counsel,Mix of underwriting-omission and governance/voting items.
