19,"The xAI merger became effective February 2, 2026 and the X merger March 28, 2025. For how many months of FY2025 was each entity included on an actual-close basis, and what analytical challenge does retrospective recast accounting create?",quantitative,Accounting and common-control recast mechanics,,Accounting and transaction advisory,Actual-close vs recast timing.
