21,"When evaluating future orbital AI compute satellites, which disclosed accounting policies or asset categories provide the closest precedent for treatment? Does the filing explicitly resolve whether such assets would be capitalized or expensed?",disclosure,Execution and program risk,Accounting and common-control recast mechanics,Accounting and transaction advisory,Forward capex treatment / accounting-policy precedent.
