24,"AI segment capex totaled $7,723M in Q1 2026. Annualize this figure and compare it with annualized AI revenue. What does the comparison imply about near-term free cash flow pressure and capital intensity?",quantitative,Capital intensity and funding,,Credit analysis,FCF pressure / capital-intensity stress check.
